race.description: Haras Des Trottuers The Great Square Mbl Trot G1
race.comment: Star Victorian mare KEAYANG ZAHARA (9) looks a class above these. She scored another effortless win in the Vicbred 4M Super Series Final at Melton last start, taking her record to a phenomenal 19 from 20. Won both tries at this distance and with clear air from her draw on the back row should be scoring again. SUNSET HILL NZ (12) draws awkwardly and tackles a topliner tonight but is on the up having easily won his two Menangle starts since switching from New Zealand. AJAY VOLSTEAD (10) came from this row for a second-up win at this circuit and distance last week. This is much stronger but he could progress further. MAORIS MAC (5) has been more than 14m behind KEAYANG ZAHARA when runner-up in her last two outings but can get into the exotics.
